    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You shouldn't need this code at all. None of the negotiation code or ICE code should be blocking forever on close (or else we have bigger problems), and the unlocks are deferred so it should be fine.\r\n\r\nThis is what causes the panics btw",
